Package org.springframework.geode.boot.autoconfigure.configuration.support

Class PoolProperties

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.geode.boot.autoconfigure.configuration.support.PoolProperties
public class PoolProperties extends Object
Spring Boot ConfigurationProperties used to configure an Apache Geode client Pool. The configuration Properties are based on well-known, documented Spring Data for Apache Geode (SDG) Properties.
Since:
1.0.0
